                <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;LEGEND&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Topology&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;PC1 — R1 (AS 65001) — R3 (AS 65002)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Single eBGP session, IPv4 only&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Link Types&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;White (w=2) — Routed P2P (/30)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;White (w=1) — Access port / LAN&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;White dashed — Logical loopback attach&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;AS Zones&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Teal dashed — AS 65001 (local)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Amber dashed — AS 65002 (peer ISP)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Interface Notation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;.N = last octet of interface IP&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Source octet hugs source device&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Target octet hugs target device&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;BGP Scope (lab-00)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;eBGP only — TCP/179&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;R1 advertises 172.16.1.0/24, 192.168.1.0/24&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;R3 advertises 172.16.3.0/24" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#000000;strokeColor=#FFFFFF;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=8;arcSize=3;" parent="1" vertex="1">
